      public static final Contact contact(String name, Object url, String email)
      Creates an Contact element with the specified name, url, and email attributes.
      Parameters:
      name - The name attribute.
      url - The url attribute.
      The value can be of any of the following types: URI, URL, String.

      URIs defined by UriResolver can be used for values.
      email - The email attribute.
      Returns:
      The new element.
